      "id": "text_formula",
      "x": 830, "y": 800,
      "width": 580, "height": 100,
      "text": "Key Formulas:\nconfidence = 0.5 × LLM_judge + 0.5 × avg_RAG_similarity\nRAG_score  = 0.5 × rerank + 0.3 × vector + 0.2 × RRF\nTruLens RAG Triad: answer_relevance + context_relevance + groundedness",
